N2  - The purpose of this note is to prove that the rules on which Theil and van de Panne [Theil, H., C. van de Panne. 1960. Quadratic programming as an extension of conventional quadratic maximization. Management Sci. 7(1) 1?20] based their recent method to follow straightforward from the well-known Kuhn-Tucker conditions and to propose a method for handling degeneracy in quadratic programming.
